        The patterns are in 8 colors only, included some topaz like fonts. The magazine promised me a copy of the issue and I'm still waiting.

@{fg shine} BNS patterns 2 @{fg text} - NOW, Aminet release

        The patterns are now in 16 colors and the full screens are in PNG, included a @{" grab from my bench " system "SYS:Utilities/Multiview SCREEN grab"}. Two patterns of the first release have been reworked and included here. These are @{" Wolf " system "SYS:Utilities/Multiview SCREEN FullScreens/Wolf"} and @{" Aigle " system "SYS:Utilities/Multiview SCREEN FullScreens/Aigle"}.

@endnode

